      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty (turbulence model selection, hemolysis power-law exponent choice) is partially addressed through the sensitivity analysis documented in the uncertainty quantification. Full model form assessment requiring alternative model comparisons is not required at MRL 2 for this COU. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3."
