      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "not-applicable",
      "rationale": "Test samples factor applies to assessments where physical test specimens are fabricated for comparison. This COU uses the FDA generic centrifugal pump as a computational geometry reference; no physical specimens were fabricated for this credibility assessment. The experimental data used for validation are from the FDA benchmark dataset, which was generated under a separate test programme. Not applicable per ASME V&V 40-2018 factor applicability guidance."
    },
